<h1>Prefixers</h1>

<p>
Prefixers are LESS mixins created to make your coding easier by adding prefixes such as <code>-webkit</code> to your styles.
</p>

<p>
So instead of writing <code>-webkit-transform: 300ms</code> and such. You can simply write <code>.lui.transition.this(300ms)</code>
and LUI will do all the work for you.
</p>

<p>
Prefixers are part of <code>LUI-3_base</code> component, because they are used across all other LUI-3 components, so they can be counted as part of its core.
</p>

